---
title: Meatball Ragu with Green Beans and Rice
description: Let’s not beat around the bush. When it comes to a comforting crowd-pleaser recipe, nothing hits the spot like a big bowl of juicy meatballs. With only 20 minutes hands on cooking time, Head Chef Andre has been working together with our beef suppliers to ensure minimum effort and maximum taste! And to keep everyone in the family happy, we’ve jazzed things up a little for the grown ups - topping your tomatoey caramelised beef meatballs with crumbled feta and parsley. Delicious!
